title: Sochi preview with Juan Manuel Correa
description: JM is back on the show to catch us up on his recovery and to look ahead to the Russian Grand Prix. Juan will be back with Alexis Nunes, Laurence Edmondson and Nate Saunders on Sunday to recap what goes down at Sochi. Stay tuned.
